{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2d18e29b66","title":"中央军委给东北局的五点指示","origin":"根据北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编 《中央首长讲话（4）》，北京：1967年5月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f26ef6c59d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":1,"articleId":"2d18e29b66"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"217d21cf1e","type":"title","text":"中共中央军委给东北局的五点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66"},{"id":"0d56516a67","type":"paragraph","text":"1、不准把群众组织任意打成反革命组织，打成反革命组织必须由中央批准。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66"},{"id":"8ba199582d","type":"paragraph","text":"2、冲击过、反对过军区，提过意见的，被捕的一律释放，通令一律作废。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66"},{"id":"c78f4a5cc9","type":"paragraph","text":"3、对违法乱纪犯罪个人依法惩办，要和群众严格区分开来。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66"},{"id":"edfcc92a28","type":"paragraph","text":"4、群众组织犯严重错误的，要通过整风开展批评与自我批评的方式来解决，不能强迫请罪、挂牌字。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66"},{"id":"9e0e3072f7","type":"paragraph","text":"5、不准在左派队伍中支持一派打击一派。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66"},{"id":"bd2e6b3ae1","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共中央军委一九六七年四月一日","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66"}],"page":{"id":"95effd8cf4","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2d18e29b66","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}